# There is a patch to fix the waddir for version 2.5.0 in the grimoire

   version stable 2.5.0 2.4.7 2.4.6
   require MesaLib SDL_mixer SDL_net doom_wad
  category game/3d
 attribute x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL prboom/prboom%20stable/$VERSION/prboom-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://prboom.sourceforge.net
      desc 'engine for running first person shooter games such as doom
Possibily due to a bug you may have to run 
it from the present working directory of:
/usr/share/games/doom
so it can find prboom.wad'
